<a href="/question/27515351">如何用 Photoshop 做出杂志封面的效果？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3188954" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">题主小摄影师一枚，前几天帮朋友拍了组片子，自认为前期还拿得出手，后期就实在素手无策了，还是得求助无所不能的知乎er！！！！！<br><br><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/ecfc034a4870d0fb5172f1ce2d7bc22f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1334" data-rawheight="2000" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/ecfc034a4870d0fb5172f1ce2d7bc22f_r.jpg"></div>


