<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="241">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-shuang-yi-58" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-shuang-yi-58" class="zg-link" title="陈双一">陈双一</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wu-zheng-yue" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wu-zheng-yue" class="zg-link" title="吴峥越">吴峥越</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yao-qing-shu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yao-qing-shu" class="zg-link" title="坠吼是窝">坠吼是窝</a></span>
