<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3188954" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/1b6c6b05c585c0b25edd109f1b9bfbd3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="427" data-rawheight="571" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="427" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/1b6c6b05c585c0b25edd109f1b9bfbd3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="427" data-rawheight="571" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="427" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/1b6c6b05c585c0b25edd109f1b9bfbd3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/1b6c6b05c585c0b25edd109f1b9bfbd3_b.jpg"><br><br>1. 找到你想要的杂志，研究其封面有哪些特点。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/145e728bd62e31dfa7b6e35a2659fee8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1338" data-rawheight="494" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1338" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/145e728bd62e31dfa7b6e35a2659fee8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1338" data-rawheight="494" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1338" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/145e728bd62e31dfa7b6e35a2659fee8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/145e728bd62e31dfa7b6e35a2659fee8_b.jpg"><br>2. 根据所总结特点，另需三步：<br><br>(1)  打开否头笑胚CS6<br><br>(2)  进行下图操作：<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/f16d4df889e90455fc9372f70b4581a5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="505" data-rawheight="377" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="505" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/f16d4df889e90455fc9372f70b4581a5_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="505" data-rawheight="377" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="505" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/f16d4df889e90455fc9372f70b4581a5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/f16d4df889e90455fc9372f70b4581a5_b.jpg"><br>(3) 退出否头笑胚CS6<br><br><br>注：<br>图层2是封面下半部分的文字，通过 [选择] -&gt; [色彩范围] 把白底去掉。<br>大标题衬于人像下方所以不用管。<br><br><br>其他杂志同理。


</div>

